{"tid":1350432,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"律師會稱正嚴正檢視對律師何君堯相關投訴","createTime":"2019-07-22T12:52:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T13:22:37.000Z","uid":240362,"like":92,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"cc72823a06b61dc552e0ce986cd6c2674662598b","tid":1350432,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T12:52:17.000Z","msg":"律師會表示，已收到對律師何君堯的投訴，正嚴正檢視相關投訴事件，如有需要會交予律師紀律審裁組處理，由於專業操守調查屬於保密，律師會暫時不作評論。公民黨前主席余若薇表示，已向律師會執業操守組投訴，要求盡快調查何君堯，懷疑他和元朗毆打事件有關。余若薇在社交平台表示互聯網流傳片段，可見酷似何君堯的人答謝懷疑毆打市民的人士，懷疑何君堯涉嫌違反《律師執業規則》。"},{"pid":"32b49ab03d35978fcd6203fb2cf0307837ed6fd7","tid":1350432,"uid":141419,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T12:56:24.000Z","msg":"香港哩刻都係言論自由<br />\n但每個人都要為自己行為言論負責<br />\n仲要係律師<br />\n各位收佢老母皮"},{"pid":"3ee6cf28fb994f300a971ec4447f0b71f87dbc7e","tid":1350432,"uid":36134,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T12:57:54.000Z","msg":"唔洗酷似<br />\n何妖都出左記招認左個晚係佢"},{"pid":"b9f6c0db3640e10f675c32b8af4b9b27ab1275d2","tid":1350432,"uid":48234,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T12:59:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">現行犯調你老母查咩<br />\n緊急宣判佢違反律師執業規則唔得?</span></span>"},{"pid":"5b68be51ecd6b9499dd503f66244489e88d26ac3","tid":1350432,"uid":145021,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T13:01:09.000Z","msg":"律師會咪又係自己友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"786531681e70d545ac1b826fe70f4d2f92d833ac","tid":1350432,"uid":103759,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T13:01:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n=================<br />\n【港鐵職員建議在港鐵遇險時如何自保/逃生】<br />\n<br />\n如沒有警察下， 在列車門沒有關上:<br />\n1) 可以試自行拉動車門關上<br />\n2) 車上有滅火筒， 請對準外面畜生 (但要緊記夠力先用, 否則會被搶去反被人扑頭)<br />\n3) 通知 車長 , 列車有煙有火， 車長必然會搵TC (traffic controller, 行車控制主任) 報警， call消防。<br />\n4) 如果 在車站內， 或 月台中， 可以按動任何消防警報器， 如沒記錯， 那個警報會直接連接消防<br />\n5) 在非常迫不得以下， 走去列車兩端的控制室， 推開緊急逃生門， 不過， 要小心路軌可能有其他列車， 雖然 emergency door一推， 車長會報TC, TC會 hold住所有列車， ( 但我唔確定 那車長會有人性報TC )  e door一推， 就會係港鐵嘅 重大事故， 冇警察實有消防救護， 就算無消防無救護， 都會有一隊MTR staff衝住嚟 <br />\n<br />\n緊記! 推 e door唔一定要走, 因為落路軌有風險, 所以推 e door係俾個訊息車長, 有人 可能落咗路軌, 但我哋會當真做, 咁個車長無得食花生睇打交!<br />\n<br />\n6) 如在站內，可以拿起滅火筒自保。 盡快逃去車站控制室， 門外有對講機， 和站長對話， 站長可以放人入內<br />\n7) 如附近有消防喉，可用水 對準畜生和禽獸。請用盡車站，月台或列車中的設施自保<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;金水Facebook"},{"pid":"59b7c136a9bb3164471cb5a0b52fe582d5981981","tid":1350432,"uid":34415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T13:01:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/520eo1h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F520eo1h.jpg&h=32ecfa79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SMbASUF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSMbASUF.jpg&h=a2ce6deb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kjPbreK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkjPbreK.jpg&h=068b8664&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tKrX6eR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtKrX6eR.jpg&h=922f47ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/87OcaGA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F87OcaGA.jpg&h=5d1b1e66&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"697a2fac12b46ee68bc5ec95833103252350dc21","tid":1350432,"uid":260367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3ee6cf28fb994f300a971ec4447f0b71f87dbc7e","tid":1350432,"uid":36134,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"20